eloped its diagnostic test and <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Hepatitis_B_vaccine\" title=\"Hepatitis B vaccine\">vaccine<\/a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-nobel_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Baruch_S._Blumberg#cite_note-nobel-2\"><span>[<\/span>2<span>]<\/span><\/a><\/sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Baruch_S._Blumberg#cite_note-3\"><span>[<\/span>3<span>]<\/span><\/a><\/sup><\/p>","name":"Baruch S. Blumberg","place_of_birth":"Brooklyn, New York","place_of_death":"Mountain View ,  California , U.S.","text":"Baruch S. Blumberg , Physiology or Medicine, 1976","year":1976.0}